                            <comment id="14456690" author="rsmith86" created="Sat, 28 Feb 2015 13:59:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I created a pull request to show where the problem in the code seems to be. &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/86&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/pull/86&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14456657" author="rsmith86" created="Sat, 28 Feb 2015 15:31:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I updated the sample project. After initial basic tests i found that surefire can not handle non default parameter test descriptions properly. It scrambles the method name on the ( character. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test3 and Test4 are an example for that behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
